      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 10.2 - 老子 10.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 10.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>能無離乎？專氣致柔，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When one gives undivided attention to the (vital) breath, and brings it to the utmost degree of pliancy, he can become as a (tender) babe.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
