      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 10.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>能嬰兒乎？滌除玄覽，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When he has cleansed away the most mysterious sights (of his imagination), he can become without a flaw.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
