      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 10.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>能無疵乎？愛國治民，能無知乎？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In loving the people and ruling the state, cannot he proceed without any (purpose of) action?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
