      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 10.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天門開闔，能為雌乎？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the opening and shutting of his gates of heaven, cannot he do so as a female bird?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
