      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 10.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>明白四達，能無為乎？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>While his intelligence reaches in every direction, cannot he (appear to) be without knowledge?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
